      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAINT KYLIE (2) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 305m behind Aston Deutz (18.14) in a Grade 6. Was in the money the start prior. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Should bounce back. OPAL LIMES (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (31.20) in a Grade 6 at this track. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. PICK A CADILLAC (8) finished second (18.46) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 6th there. One of the main contenders. MOCAMBORA JACK (4) makes debut for the Scott Blacksell kennel. No favours with the draw and will need to begin well. Can run a bold race on debut.",
